  "texts": [
    "The only exception is the Scoring Strategy on the MARBLE dataset, where the score obtained by GPT3.5 on Model Prototypes is only 1% higher than the one obtained on LIME.",
    "These results suggests that, in order to reduce costs, even simpler and cheaper model can approximate user surveys.",
    "In this work, we introduced the novel idea of using LLMs to automatically evaluate natural language explanations of XAI methods for sensor-based HAR.",
    "Our preliminary experiments show that our prompting strategies make it possible to leverage LLMs to obtain a quantitative assessment that is consistent with more challenging user surveys.",
    "This is still a preliminary investigation, and we have several plans for future work."
